.// File:  bridge.mark
.//
.// Description:
.// This marking file is used to specify inter-domain brige wiring to the
.// model compiler.
.//
.// IMPORTANT NOTE:
.// All references to a domain name in this file corrospond to the registered
.// domain name, and NOT the BridgePoint domain repository name.
.// Domain names are registered in the 'registry.mark' marking file via the
.// RegisterOoaDomain function.
.//
